  <span id="freeText5238869474912622697" style="display:none">This book is a mesmerizing magic trick! It's like you're watching a shell game and trying to track all of the cups in rotation. Except the cups are couplings. <br /><br />Also, you find out very early that 'unicorn' is a euphemism for penis. Saucy!</span>
