pljivanju savesti i raskolu razuma i srca... Dubok, nadahnjujuć, pisan u dve vremenske ravni koje se virtuozno prepliću, uz riznicu najrazličitijih karaktera, bogat dekor i arhaičan jezik kojim autorka maestralno oživljava prošlost, roman Evgenija Hajden nas vraća u svet davno zaboravljenih ruskih i domaćih klasika i otkriva nadarenog pisca.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"741943175583407210\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'14_book_29915049\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"08+M6xcoC3ngKiwE1f1CFsU0mI6i0fEyAUT3DiTRoxUkJ8DKD7CWKstrm+7oVfYL4dg0jKjtYr5Q0iJtvB5y3Q==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"29915049\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"14_book_29915049\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/89788.The_Lady_and_the_Unicorn\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\n<span class=\'progressTrigger\'>Want to Read<\/span>\n<span class=\'progressIndicator\'>saving…<\/span>\n<\/button>\n<\/form>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\'wtrRight wtrUp\'>\n<form