ith her boisterous German lover and confused husband. And the young tearaway Xavier, in love with the virginal Agnes.\n\nOver a million Rose Tremain books sold\n\n‘A writer of exceptional talent ... Tremain is a writer who understands every emotion’ Independent I\n\n‘There are few writers out there with the dexterity or emotional intelligence to rival that of the great Rose Tremain’ Irish Times\n\n‘Tremain has the painterly genius of an Old Master, and she uses it to stunning effect’ The Times\n\n‘Rose Tremain is one of the very finest British novelists’ Salman Rushdie\n\n‘Tremain is a writer of exemplary vision and particularity. The fictional world is rendered with extraordinary vividness’ Marcel Theroux, Guardian<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"2837139762796904215\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'25_book_1099560\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"i6Bsh46oYb63f/kvQkVsH+SWgWM7Ve7BsxHICadNTxF8SCCmljD87Zw+TsV/7dgCwHotYTFpfU3ihx1qP4Ke2Q==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"1099560\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"25_book_1099560\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=